announcements: There may be members of our ward who are not recieving communications or the order of services. We invite all ministers to please check in the ward directory that your ministering families have a household email address, and if they don't to please help them to set one up. Please contact Brother Flaherty if you need assistance.
Choir practice will resume beginning after church in the Relief Society room at 1:15.

Our Stake has organized a single adult committee for single members of our stake between the ages of 31 - 45. We are in need of a committee representative from our ward to participate in planning events and activities, if you have interest in serving in this capacity please reach out to a member of the bishopric.

The annual Kimball Stake Relief Society Event is coming up in two weeks on February 28, 2023 at 6:30 at the Stake Center.  We are having a Stake Service Night. We will be working on 12 JustServe Projects.  We will also be having a light dinner while the sisters serve.
